lines: grub rigs shar gyi ri bo'i rtser
rgyal sras kun dga'i zla ba ni
'phrin las bzang po'i bsil zer can
sgrub brgyud bstan pa'i ku mud gnyen
don yod sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan ni
srid rtse'i bar du sgreng mkhas pa
gang de dus gsum mkhyen pa zhes
grags pa 'jig rten gsum na dkar
mkhyen rab kun dga'i gzhal med khang
legs bshad rin cen tshogs kyis gang
bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan mthon po can
deng 'dir skal bzang yongs kyi mgon
gang gi drin las sku gsum go 'phang yang
skal bzang gdul bya'i lag rtser skad cig gis
sbyin mdzad de ni e ma'o skyabs kyi mchog
bstod cing bsngags 'os de las gzhan na gang
de slad bla ma mchog gi yon tan gyi
rin cen 'byung gnas pha mtha' bral ba las
ngo mtshar 'od chags sdeb legs mu tig phreng
skal bzang mdzes ma'i mgul rgyan bdag gis spel
gang gi rnam dpyod yangs pa'i chu mthongs ngos
grangs med legs bshad dbyar skyes phreng ba can
snyan tshig 'brug sgra dal gyis dgod pa na
thar 'dod gtsug phud can rnams gar byos shig
bgrang yas mkhas grub zhabs mthil gur gum tshon
reg pas 'phags pa'i yul la'ang co 'dri ba
rnam mang grong khyer rin cen ba gam gyi
'od tshogs ga bur rtse dga' dgod pa can
sa la gnas kyang mtho ris 'jig rten gyi
chos kyis mtho ba'i pho brang byang phyogs 'dir
dal gyis zhugs 'dra dben pa'i bsti gnas cher
'jig rten mig gyur rgyal sras chu mdangs gang
grub pa'i pho nya yum gyi chu 'dzin las
srid pa'i rtse mor 'phur lding zlos gar mkhan
grub pa'i dbang pos cod pan btud nas kyang
rgyal sras kun dga'i zla bar khyod lung bstan
gsung rab klog sogs mtha' med shes bya'i khyon
khyod thugs mkhyen pa'i r+wa bar chud pa na
rab tu skyengs ldan brtan g.yo'i dngos po kun
rang bzhin stong pa'i dbyings su bros sam snyam
kun gyi bshes gnyen slob dpon dang bral yang
gtsug lag nor 'dzin ma lus blo gros kyi
gom pa gcig gis gsal bar 'gongs pa na
nyi ma'i gnyen de'ang zhi ba'i dbyings su gzims
smin legs yid srubs myos bum gzung 'os pa
bcu phrag 'dab 'phreng g.yo ba'i chu skyes las
gnag snum lhung bzed bar gyi bung ba ni
nges par chags bral 'doms byed bla mar gyur
snying ni tshangs spyod bdud rtsis gang gyur pa'i
gser gyi sa 'dzin bzhin du de mthong nas
ngur mo rgyags pa'i khyu bzhin drang srong tshogs
lhun po'i bang rim ngos su bros pa bzhin
blo bzang 'dzam bu tri sha'i rkang 'thung gi
'bras bzang sngon med legs bshad ro brgya pa
ma dros dbang po gzhan bzhin mgon khyod kyis
'dod rgur spyad bya'i tsi Ta nyid du gyur
rgyas pa rgan po'i lugs 'dzin drang srong gi
spyi bor 'jigs med zhabs sen ngal gso ba
phul byung rnam dpyod mdzes ma'i mtshar sdug ni
mkhas rnams snying la dpyid kyi dga' ston nyid
yab rje dri bral thugs kyi me long la
ches phra'i lam gyi gnad kun mngon sum du
snang tshe mngon shes lnga ldan drang srong rnams
gser gyi ri ngogs 'bros las 'os ci yod
dam pa'i zhabs sen zla ba'i 'od
spyi bo'i gzhi la lhung gyur pa
de yi mod la kun rmongs kyi
mun pa'i dgra sde ring du song
gzhung lugs nyi zla'i rna cha dang
man ngag rgyu skar do shal can
sngo bsangs ma 'dis 'chi med lam
khengs pa thung ngur byed pa bzhin
legs bshad ma li'i dog pa can
rnam dpyod tsu ta'i rkang 'thung gi
dri bzang blo gsal bung ba'i tshogs
mgron du 'bod la rings pa bzhin
mi bzad 'gro rnams nyes spyod gzugs can bzhin
tsha zer zol gyis 'dzin ma'i lo tog rnams
thal bar byas tshe thugs rje'i lha lam las
glo bur nyid du dbyar skyes sngon po'i phreng
srid gsum glog gi mtshon chas 'debs pa bzhin
'brug sgra phyogs kun dgod pa'i gad mo bzhin
skye rgu'i bsod nams bzhin du bdud rtsi'i char
drag tu phab tshe 'gro 'di'i re ba dang
mnyam du 'dzin ma'i khyon kun gang bar byas
na tshod gsar pa'i zla tshes ches phra yang
grub pa'i mtshan ma'i 'od dkar stong 'gyed pa
gang 'di'i ngo mtshar bsngags byed ut+pal phreng
phyogs kyi bu mo'i mgrin par gar byed do
mgon khyod spyi bor bkod nas dbang bskur ba
de tshe ston ka'i sprin dkar zur phud dang
rab 'grogs rin cen ri bo'i dpal phrogs gyur
phul byung yon tan nor bu'i rkang stegs kyis
'jigs med chos kyi gdan khri la 'dzegs pa
gang der bgrang yas grub pa'i cod pan gyis
zhabs sen nor bu'i me long ci yang mdzes
de tshe 'dzum dkar zhal gyi chu skyes la
phul byung legs bshad sbrang rtsi'i bcud chags pas
skal bzang rkang drug ldan pa'i tshogs rnams kun
rab dga'i gar gyis chu mthongs 'gog pa bzhin
phul byung dad pa'i rtsibs stong sngon 'gro ba'i
'dun pa brtson 'grus dran dang shes rab kyi
yan lag bzhi ldan dpung pa'i shugs 'chang ba
khyod kyis bstan pa'i sa chen dbang du byas
cha yis nyal 'gro'i rgyun kun der gzhol ba
de ni mkhas dang grub pa'i legs bshad kyi
klung 'bum sdud byed khyod thugs zla bas 'phel
'phrog byed mig stong ldan yang bshol med mar
chags las drang srong dmod pas bskrun pa ste
legs spyad goms pa'i mthu las chos kyi spyan
padma'i 'dab ldan rgyas la su yis 'gran
gdengs can ral pa'i klong du nor lha ni
gnyid gyur yongs 'du'i sring mo'i gdung dbyangs bzhin
ngo mtshar thub pa'i legs bshad sgra brgya pas
khyod thugs chu skyar mdzes ma'i brtan pa phrogs
ha ri'i rkang 'thung rlung bzhon gyis bskyod cing
ri dwags gzhon nu'i mig zur ut+pal dag
spro bzhin rnga ma'i rlung yab g.yo ba can
ma la ya yi ri bo gangs can 'dir
dal gyis 'ongs 'dra dben pa'i bsti gnas su
gang gi gshog rtse g.yo ba'i 'thor rlung gis
rin cen ri bo mkhar nyal grong khyer bcas
rab tu 'dar byed rgyal ba'i ye shes lnga
'dab bzang dbang po'i gar gyis rnam rol bas
mi bzad sder mo'i kyo bas lag 'gro'i snying
phye mar byas tshe rgyal sras 'od dkar can
nyer 'tshe'i mun can dgra las rgyal bar gyur
brkus pa'i ri dwags mo rnams mgrin 'khyog cing
ga bur dri bzang g.yo ba'i rlung bzhon gyis
'bigs byed ri bo phyogs 'dir bkug pa bzhin
mkha' la sprin dkar gsar pa'i phang phung du
'khrul pa'i 'dab bzang tshogs rnams gar byed cing
lhun stug zla shel ba gam brtsegs pa'i ngos
bsod nams brgya pa'i mig 'phrul man+d+ha ra'i
gzi 'bar cir yang 'char ba'i snang brnyan gyis
rab gsal nor bu'i me long nye ba
brtan g.yo'i dngos kun bde stong rol par ni
'char ba'i ting 'dzin sgo brgya 'byed mthong nas
nyon mongs mun pa'i tshogs bzhin mda' lnga pa
stobs ldan bzhin du mya ngan sa 'og zhugs
zla nyi mtshams kyi mun pa'i sgrib g.yogs dang
bral ba'i mkha' dbyings rtag tu gnyid gyur las
sad tshe khyod sku rin cen za ma tog
sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i nor bus ci yang mdzes

thigs pas legs bran mkhyen yangs 'dab brgya pa
mi zad legs bshad sbrang rtsi'i 'byung gnas de
skal bzang rkang drug ldan pa'i nyer 'tshor gyur

mtha' dag shes bya'i mkha' lam kun khyab pa'i
sngon med blo gros dbyar skyes 'phreng ba las

rta ljang shing rtas ma drangs shing
shar ri'i rtse las ma byung yang
'gro 'di cig car snang byed pa'i
nam mkha'i nor bu 'di ngo mtshar
phul byung mkhyen dgongs dag pa'i me long ngo
bsod nams brgya pa'i mtshar sdug gang snang ba
